<p>Should you keep iTunes on your boot drive? If not, then where? How best to migrate from a PowerPC to an Intel Mac? How do I monitor bandwidth that each application on my Mac is using? Why won&#39;t images appear in my email? &nbsp;All these questions are answered &#8212; and even more tips are shared &#8212; in this week&#39;s episode of The Mac Geek Gab with John F. Braun and Dave Hamilton.</p>
<p>Note: Shownotes are complete!</p>
